{"id": 64, "genre": 1000, "title": "Apple Watch来了，你还有什么想不通的？", "description": "苹果终于出智能手表了——Apple Watch是一款可以与 iPhone 连接的可穿戴设备，兼具健康追踪与通讯功能。该款产品售价 349 美元，将于 2015 年初上市。\r\n", "record_count": 5514, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606061619161Zi4vGtw0uJafF2e.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-09-10T09:58:52Z", "questions": [{"id": 80, "title": "Apple Watch来了，你还有什么想不通的？", "content": "Apple Watch来了，你现在还有什么想不通的？", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 706, "content": "用手表打电话效果好吗", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161810MfakN8jyZ4BzEhwe.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 707, "content": "需要总是充电吗", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161810pmtkAgCfw5uclMZX.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 708, "content": "那么小的屏幕上到底可以干嘛？", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161810wW3Z9npQjKGElhqU.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 709, "content": "会又大又笨重吗？", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161810j8F6waUKd51RLHer.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 710, "content": "到底有什么新的社交功能？", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161810fkvhwLtX5ReBxm6V.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 711, "content": "想做睡眠监测的，戴着睡觉难受不？", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161811VueINtUl3gOR4G8f.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 712, "content": "有没有高级的测量仪器？", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161811E8kuaRQINo9zUjLf.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 713, "content": "需要卖肾吗？", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161811Tceo73JdaKLU6kCl.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}